description: Turn heads with this spectacular mud cake. This easy recipe layers two of our rocky road mudcakes with chocolate frosting and crunchy, gooey toppings.
name: Loaded Rocky Road Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 190 g Woolworths rocky road mallow biscuits

recipeInstructions.text: Decorate top of cake with biscuits, marshmallows, peanuts and half of the raspberries. Serve with remaining raspberries.
